開支增加係因為綜援居港限制由7年改做1年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw,睇返個表，其實每年新移民家庭申請綜援數目冇少到，都係大約總數10%到，只係政府批少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為本身新移民家庭可以靠個仔女去申請綜援(單非)，&ldquo;7變1&ldquo;根本唔會減少新移民家庭申請綜援數目，反而係增加左綜援個開支<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7bd7b5a4728255308bc05b6a3109f64aa840e7","tid":1030066,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"永遠7年後 變做香港人<br />\n<br />\n個分子永遠都係呢個數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a052c642e658608c452fb534fcad2b6f11bbb3bb","tid":1030066,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}